description:
Daniel Lopatin debuts for Warp with an eagerly awaited ninth solo album. 

'R Plus 7' follows the increasingly complex vectors of his 'Returnal' and 'Replica' sides with an ambitious fervor, scoping ten dazzling planes of hyper-reality framing analog/digital productions.
